OL,5, Facebook-owner Meta has warned of      
OL,6, slowing growth, as audiences flock to  
OL,7, competitors like TikTok and the        
OL,8, businesses that advertise on its       
OL,9, platforms cut marketing budgets.       
OL,11,FThe firm said sales growth could be    
OL,12,Fjust 3% in the first three months of   
OL,13,F2022, far below its historic pace.     
OL,15,FProfits have already been hit as the   
OL,16,Ffirm ploughs money into projects       
OL,17,Ffocused on virtual reality.            
OL,19,FThe update sent shares down 20% in     
OL,20,Fafter-hours trade.                     
